            hi
        % elif y+7==10:
            there
        % elif lala:
            lala
        % else:
            hi
        % endif
"""

""",
    (5, 1)), ControlLine('elif', 'elif lala:', False, (6, 1)), Text(
    '            lala\n', (7, 1)), ControlLine('else', 'else:', False, (8, 
    1)), Text('            hi\n', (9, 1)), ControlLine('if', 'endif', True,
    (10, 1))]))
